{"tid":257051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"黑幫變丐幫 淪落到超市偷米偷西瓜 日本山口組成員：組織缺錢","createTime":"2017-05-25T03:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T06:42:27.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78dc663b87c2f790286c6d2b058428d068770fb4","tid":257051,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495597327_2e2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495597327_2e2b.jpg&h=631c7afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本愛知縣名古屋市三名山口組系的成員，因為在超市盜竊食品及日用品等被捕，他們直言因組織資金資乏，「為組織繼續生存」而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上月23日，當地時間下午7時20分左右，55歲組長郡司真人，帶同59歲幹部中島良輔以及52歲的飯田廣，齊齊到一間商場的超市盜竊。三人偷走西瓜、鰻魚、米共198件，總值76,120日圓（約5,300港元）的食品及日用品。郡司同日被捕，縣警周二發表中島及飯田被捕的消息。<br />\n<br />\n同為無業的中島及飯田承認犯案，中島直言：「組的營運資金緊絀，為了令組繼續生存下去，金錢是必要的。」<br />\n<br />\n日本山口組在戰後混亂時間，曾有過「輝煌歲月」，當年是收入高達數十億美元的犯罪組織，涉獵色情、賭業及毒品交易。與中國的三合會組織或意大利黑手黨不同，他們並不違法，一直受警方監管，曾被視為「維繫地方街頭秩序的必要邪惡勢力」。<br />\n<br />\n但近年經濟疲弱、社會容忍度降低及成員人數減少的情況下，當地黑幫越來越難生存。政府收緊反黑幫條例，令黑幫成員連開銀行戶口都難。這些因素被指是山口組高調分裂的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n日本朝日新聞/法新社"},{"pid":"62cdd21e28e1634e50d579d25d9a721549bb8af0","tid":257051,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4873f55c131518dbbdf5ceff199034184f74686b","tid":257051,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"山口組組長 洪七公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ce15aaba2b2ba2e90409b07fae819a55fcfc6d","tid":257051,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b2f5d17179cc9497dbe9c08d8affcacbd0962c","tid":257051,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cd79e4e0c14ba112496e0380dd1e601ae7274a","tid":257051,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"似廢老多過黑幫"}]}